OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1777061157
OL,3,CAlliance MLA Kellie Armstrong
OL,4,Cannounces she will not seek re-election
OL,6,FAlliance Party MLA Kellie Armstrong
OL,7,Fhas said she will retire from politics
OL,8,Fnext year.
OL,10,FThe Strangford representative
OL,11,Fconfirmed she would not be standing in
OL,12,Fthe 2027 Assembly election.
OL,14,FMs Armstrong was first elected to the
OL,15,FAssembly in 2016, having previously
OL,16,Fbeen a councillor.
OL,18,F"It has truly been an honour to serve
OL,19,Fthe people of Strangford on behalf of
OL,20,FAlliance," she said.
OL,26,@zD@AOU|D@JO]
