OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1777061157
OL,3,CAlliance MLA Kellie Armstrong
OL,4,Cannounces she will not seek re-election
OL,6,F"I have been thinking about retiring
OL,7,Ffor a while, and so it was with great
OL,8,Fsadness I made the decision the 2027
OL,9,Felection is the right time for me to
OL,10,Fretire from politics.
OL,12,F"I will continue as an MLA, with my
OL,13,Fcolleague Nick Mathison, to serve
OL,14,FStrangford constituents until the
OL,15,Fdissolution of the Assembly, and
OL,16,Fpromise I and my constituency staff
OL,17,Fwill continue to give 100% for all
OL,18,Fthose who need help in the meantime."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUzD@eO]
