PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1777061157
OL,3,CAlliance MLA Kellie Armstrong
OL,4,Cannounces she will not seek re-election
OL,6,FMs Armstrong highlighted the
OL,7,FIntegrated Education Bill, which she
OL,8,Fintroduced to the Assembly, as a
OL,9,Fpolitical high, while saying threats
OL,10,Fand abuse she has received online were
OL,11,Fa low.
OL,13,FShe added: "I want to thank every
OL,14,Fsingle person who voted for me over
OL,15,Fthe years and allowed me the privilege
OL,16,Fof representing them over the years.
OL,26,@uD@LOU
