PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1777061157
OL,3,CAlliance MLA Kellie Armstrong
OL,4,Cannounces she will not seek re-election
OL,6,F"I will continue to be involved with
OL,7,Fthe party, and wish Nick and my
OL,8,Fsuccessor every best wish in serving
OL,9,Fthe people of this great constituency
OL,10,Fto the highest possible standards."
